de.unipassau.im.ontoint.model
Class WrappedOWLOntologyManager

java.lang.Object
  de.unipassau.im.ontoint.model.WrappedOWLOntologyManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyLoaderListener
public final class WrappedOWLOntologyManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyLoaderListener

The main entry point to the model. The WrappedOWLOntologyManager wraps an OWL API OWLOntologyManager and handles the loading and removing of WrappedOWLOntologys.

Author:
Philipp Nolte
